ad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fdb1800e23272cd3bd0425ceb890cd08a0fc8af5","tid":274112,"uid":13138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T09:14:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>三大靈場<br />\n不過我覺得似靈氣多過詭異</blockquote><br />\n恐山?"},{"pid":"62d53bdf313d0067ce6eac9785d57205cbcd7a71","tid":274112,"uid":45684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T09:16:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>三大靈場<br />\n不過我覺得似靈氣多過詭異</blockquote><br />\n恐山?</blockquote><br />\n恐山, 高野山, 比叡山"},{"pid":"3ccb2ecd01f9a3e45e71918a45daa3a178837281","tid":274112,"uid":9708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T09:17:27.000Z","msg":"如月車站 去到既話"},{"pid":"c8c6bd2497b0397941d420536cab3eaaf44d33e3","tid":274112,"uid":117596,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T09:20:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>三大靈場<br />\n不過我覺得似靈氣多過詭異</blockquote><br />\n恐山?</blockquote><br />\n恐山, 高野山, 比叡山</blockquote><br />\n恐山好正咁, 好想去<br />\n但交通好似唔方便"},{"pid":"234297d3f76b29ed62572828999b20201cf21f8c","tid":274112,"uid":45684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T09:21:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>三大靈場<br />\n不過我覺得似靈氣多過詭異</blockquote><br />\n恐山?</blockquote><br />\n恐山, 高野山, 比叡山</blockquote><br />\n恐山好正咁, 好想去<br />\n但交通好似唔方便</blockquote><br />\n去過高野, 信長個墓好細 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"383966fd261c3852931890a0cfd51596df761de2","tid":274112,"uid":13138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T09:23:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>三大靈場<br />\n不過我覺得似靈氣多過詭異</blockquote><br />\n恐山?</blockquote><br />\n恐山, 高野山, 比叡山</blockquote><br />\n恐山好正咁, 好想去<br />\n但交通好似唔方便</blockquote><br />\n去過高野, 信長個墓好細 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都好想去恐山<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n諗住遲d自己去"},{"pid":"091c5e17de290bea061e9ff456475882a5b4a5f9","tid":274112,"uid":73231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T09:41:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>三大靈場<br />\n不過我覺得似靈氣多過詭異</blockquote><br />\n恐山?</blockquote><br />\n恐山, 高野山, 比叡山</blockquote><br />\n恐山好正咁, 好想去<br />\n但交通好似唔方便</blockquote><br />\n去過高野, 信長個墓好細 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都好想去恐山<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n諗住遲d自己去</blockquote><br />\n上過比叡山睇紅葉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n冇乜特別 但我個人對靈異嘢係好遲鈍<br />\n<br />\n主要係去睇紫式部<br />\n紅葉好靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n因為某些原因冇留底同相（你懂的）<br />\n但同下面網站講嘅行程差唔多<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.xuite.net/blog/devin.lu0214/twblog/359668745\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.xuite.net%2Fblog%2Fdevin.lu0214%2Ftwblog%2F359668745&d=RqhwnB06MJQCJkBLgkiVqviMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=2aea4a9a\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.xuite.net/blog/devin.lu0214/twblog/359668745</a><br />\n未去過嘅真係值得去嘅"},{"pid":"abb39e1459940fca152daffad26f5d4869eae845","tid":274112,"uid":47565,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T09:45:14.000Z","msg":"個陣落雪去青木原<br />\n又綠又白咁好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/09/174510_d33f7455915cbc85b5b0bcdb08d6b515.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F09%2F174510_d33f7455915cbc85b5b0bcdb08d6b515.jpg&h=d30ee28a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c175d373ad50e8f44f62a8f88d1b5503ee80ef4f","tid":274112,"uid":88167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T09:54:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://image.ibb.co/ccmpdF/20160527_002148.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage.ibb.co%2FccmpdF%2F20160527_002148.jpg&h=b29dd120&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://image.ibb.co/kH7ZCa/20160527_001311.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage.ibb.co%2FkH7ZCa%2F20160527_001311.jpg&h=700bfde6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://image.ibb.co/cFx1sa/20160527_010659.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage.ibb.co%2FcFx1sa%2F20160527_010659.jpg&h=527389cd&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n屌，夜晚比入架咩sosad<br />\n行完千本鳥居，落山中段出去果堆（即你第3張圖），我果陣去，落勁大雨，行哂雷，得我一個，勁撚詭異<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4252030991b30c4f15a7638aead59d85300f1ec","tid":274112,"uid":442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T09:59:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>上次去東京去開河口湖有諗住去埋青木原 但諗諗下驚出唔返黎就冇去到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n去過無講到咁詭異, 綠樹遮天見唔到太陽, 風吹過好似有海浪聽咁, 幾舒服。加上四圍差唔多樣, 悶悶地行住都覺得眼瞓<br />\n覺得係都市傳說吹大</blockquote><br />\n樹海夜晚我真係唔敢去<br />\n始終d傳說唔係全部作出黎<br />\n之前一年搵成百幾條件死屍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我唔會信個個到最後一刻都係決心尋死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\n日頭我諗我都要fd一齊先敢入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我上次去樹海見到有擺好左既鞋<br />\n十幾廿包煙盒同煙頭<br />\n重有個袋同外套<br />\n但見唔到條屍<br />\n<br />\n目標達成<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b465610980efdedcccb381e8b71cbf7553cc7760","tid":274112,"uid":13138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T11:12:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://image.ibb.co/ccmpdF/20160527_002148.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage.ibb.co%2FccmpdF%2F20160527_002148.jpg&h=b29dd120&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://image.ibb.co/kH7ZCa/20160527_001311.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage.ibb.co%2FkH7ZCa%2F20160527_001311.jpg&h=700bfde6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://image.ibb.co/cFx1sa/20160527_010659.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage.ibb.co%2FcFx1sa%2F20160527_010659.jpg&h=527389cd&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n屌，夜晚比入架咩sosad<br />\n行完千本鳥居，落山中段出去果堆（即你第3張圖），我果陣去，落勁大雨，行哂雷，得我一個，勁撚詭異<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n比入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我去個日都有毛毛雨,上到頂仲幾大霧<br />\n最後搵唔到黎個條路,見有路就落,好彩係另一條路落返山<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"719272097c0f3d9f0c3b4965681dedd8d6976b2a","tid":274112,"uid":5218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T12:56:03.000Z","msg":"慰靈之森"},{"pid":"d8f01bfda04b54395e97e5aedf8ddae411530d56","tid":274112,"uid":14591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T15:28:05.000Z","msg":"犬鳴隧道"},{"pid":"1f687f1f8c62224bdb2397fd51dbb16451cadb1f","tid":274112,"uid":73231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T11:52:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>犬鳴隧道</blockquote><br />\n呢個好似嘅幾吸引<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過係咪封曬啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}